Text: In this section, you will be presented with a series of words. Please study each word carefully. Your memory will be tested! Click next to continue.
As you study, you will be asked to rate your ability to remember each word on a later test using a 0-100 scale.

For example, if you see the word "dog", a rating of 0 means you would not expect to remember this word at test, while a rating of 100 means you would definitely remember it. When making these ratings, it is important that you try to be as accurate as possible. Try to use the full range of the scale -- Don't just make ratings of only 0 or 100!
